# Session Log

Chronological record of sessions. Add an entry at the end of each session.

**Format:**

```
## [YYYY-MM-DD] session | Brief one-line summary

### Task
What you were asked to do.

### What Happened
Key events, discoveries, decisions, failures.

### Key Learnings
What you will carry forward. Use wikilinks to reference pages you updated.
```

